metadata.recording_metadata_summary: This recording is from a middle-school participating in the PLUS tutoring program. This school is called Jackson. Students in this school use iPads to access Zoom and generally use the math software IXL. The teacher in the classroom is named Bobeck & Co., although other teachers may be present. The tutor assigned to this classroom is named Paisley Crawford, although other tutors may be present.
